"A.P.238/4/9/12:00": "...The atmosphere has changed. Perhaps there's a powerful enemy here at the end."
"But somehow with you I don't feel nervous. Actually it's quite reassuring to work with you."
"By the way, I forgot to say something. Thank you for collaborating with me. I am grateful to you."
"Partnering with you for this tournament helped me realize something."
"Since Dark Falz was revived, it's likely that we'll face harsher battles in the future."
"But working together as ARKS, I'm sure that we'll be able to overcome anything that comes at us."
"You helped remind me of that. ...That's why I thank you."
"Sorry for trailing off on a tangent. OK, let's go. This is the end."
